lead_paragraph: Josh Jackson had 22 points, Frank Mason III and Devonte Graham were nearly as productive and No. 5 Kansas rolled to an 83-63 victory over Alabama-Birmingham in the CBE Classic semifinals Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Jackson Leads No. 5 Kansas Past UAB 83-63 in CBE Classic
